@Reasoning:
Verifies XHTML-style self-closing void element (<br />). Catches a
parser regression where /> at end-of-tag isn't recognized as the void
terminator.
@End Reasoning

@Implementation:
Increment total. Build "<br />". Translator with 0 arena. Branch on
hir != 0; free source on both paths.
@End Implementation

@TestCases:
- Input "<br />" -> non-null HIR with void-element flag, passed += 1
- Parser expects "</br>" close -> translator may still succeed
- Translator returns 0 on /> sentinel -> failed += 1
@End TestCases

