@Reasoning:
Verifies <!-- ... --> comment translation. Comments may be preserved
or dropped, but they must not cause the translator to fail. Catches a
lexer regression where <!- is not recognized as the comment opener.
@End Reasoning

@Implementation:
Increment total. Build "<!-- This is a comment -->". Translator with
0 arena. Branch on hir != 0; free source on both paths.
@End Implementation

@TestCases:
- Input "<!-- This is a comment -->" -> non-null HIR, passed += 1
- Lexer mis-parses the <!-- opener -> translator returns 0 -> failed += 1
@End TestCases

